{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/2024_03_20_devridge/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h1>주요 포인트</h1>\n<p>이번 글에서는</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>프로젝트 소개 및 진행 과정</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>성과, 문제와 해결</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>아쉬운 점</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>에 대해 이야기 해보겠습니다.</p>\n<h1>프로젝트 소개</h1>\n<p>DEVRIDGE는 채용 공고와 학습 과정을 결합하여 <strong>맞춤형 학습 로드맵</strong>을 제공하고 학습 자료(영상, 책)를 소개하는 서비스 입니다.</p>\n<h2>프로젝트 관리</h2>\n<br>\r\n<center>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 462px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ad125f7eb8fa273f5929bf16be7e88dd/a9e02/devridge_1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.541666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ad125f7eb8fa273f5929bf16be7e88dd/a59e9/devridge_1.webp 192w,\n/static/ad125f7eb8fa273f5929bf16be7e88dd/0ca9f/devridge_1.webp 384w,\n/static/ad125f7eb8fa273f5929bf16be7e88dd/0b6e4/devridge_1.webp 462w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 462px) 100vw, 462px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ad125f7eb8fa273f5929bf16be7e88dd/3b721/devridge_1.png 192w,\n/static/ad125f7eb8fa273f5929bf16be7e88dd/66595/devridge_1.png 384w,\n/static/ad125f7eb8fa273f5929bf16be7e88dd/a9e02/devridge_1.png 462w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 462px) 100vw, 462px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ad125f7eb8fa273f5929bf16be7e88dd/a9e02/devridge_1.png\"\n            alt=\"Jira\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</center>\r\n<br>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>이슈 등록: Jira를 사용하여 프로젝트 관련 이슈들을 등록하고 관리</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>이슈 기반 브랜치 전략: 각 등록된 이슈에 대해 고유한 브랜치를 생성하여 개발을 진행</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>개발 및 코드 리뷰: 개발이 완료된 기능은 풀 리퀘스트를 통해 동료의 코드 리뷰</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>병합: 코드 리뷰가 성공적으로 통과한 코드를 병합(merge)</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>프로젝트 구조</h2>\n<br>\r\n<center>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 688px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b9eb9e0d97561dd4b6537a24408dcd9b/39eee/devridge_3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.1875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/b9eb9e0d97561dd4b6537a24408dcd9b/a59e9/devridge_3.webp 192w,\n/static/b9eb9e0d97561dd4b6537a24408dcd9b/0ca9f/devridge_3.webp 384w,\n/static/b9eb9e0d97561dd4b6537a24408dcd9b/f5c78/devridge_3.webp 688w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/b9eb9e0d97561dd4b6537a24408dcd9b/3b721/devridge_3.png 192w,\n/static/b9eb9e0d97561dd4b6537a24408dcd9b/66595/devridge_3.png 384w,\n/static/b9eb9e0d97561dd4b6537a24408dcd9b/39eee/devridge_3.png 688w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/b9eb9e0d97561dd4b6537a24408dcd9b/39eee/devridge_3.png\"\n            alt=\"프로젝트 아키텍처\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</center>\r\n<br>\n<h2>역할</h2>\n<h3>1. DB ERD 설계</h3>\n<br>\r\n<center>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ae2e64c77e918637e4c81225512aa2bf/a8979/devridge_2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ae2e64c77e918637e4c81225512aa2bf/a59e9/devridge_2.webp 192w,\n/static/ae2e64c77e918637e4c81225512aa2bf/0ca9f/devridge_2.webp 384w,\n/static/ae2e64c77e918637e4c81225512aa2bf/dc9b9/devridge_2.webp 768w,\n/static/ae2e64c77e918637e4c81225512aa2bf/e2c2f/devridge_2.webp 1152w,\n/static/ae2e64c77e918637e4c81225512aa2bf/f3efb/devridge_2.webp 1536w,\n/static/ae2e64c77e918637e4c81225512aa2bf/57238/devridge_2.webp 2025w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ae2e64c77e918637e4c81225512aa2bf/3b721/devridge_2.png 192w,\n/static/ae2e64c77e918637e4c81225512aa2bf/66595/devridge_2.png 384w,\n/static/ae2e64c77e918637e4c81225512aa2bf/fe486/devridge_2.png 768w,\n/static/ae2e64c77e918637e4c81225512aa2bf/d2d74/devridge_2.png 1152w,\n/static/ae2e64c77e918637e4c81225512aa2bf/e8464/devridge_2.png 1536w,\n/static/ae2e64c77e918637e4c81225512aa2bf/a8979/devridge_2.png 2025w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ae2e64c77e918637e4c81225512aa2bf/fe486/devridge_2.png\"\n            alt=\"ERD\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</center>\n<p>(이미지를 클릭하면 확대하여 볼 수 있습니다.)</p>\n<br>\n<h3>2. 회원 인증 &#x26; 인가 처리</h3>\n<p>프로젝트에서 회원 인증과 인가 처리를 담당하며, Spring Security와 OAuth2를 사용해 효율적으로 관리할 수 있는 모듈을 개발했습니다.</p>\n<p>이 모듈은 다양한 플랫폼의 인증 정보를 간단히 추가하고 적용할 수 있도록 설계되어, 새로운 인증 플랫폼을 손쉽게 등록할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">OAuth2Attribute</span> <span class=\"token function\">of</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> provider<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Map</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Object</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> attributes<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">switch</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>provider<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"google\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">ofGoogle</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>provider<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> attributes<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"kakao\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">ofKakao</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>provider<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> attributes<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">throw</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">UnsupportedProviderException</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>provider<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">OAuth2Attribute</span> <span class=\"token function\">ofGoogle</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> provider<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Map</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Object</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> attributes<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// google에서 보낸 포맷에 맞는 데이터 처리</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">OAuth2Attribute</span> <span class=\"token function\">ofKakao</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> provider<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Map</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Object</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> attributes<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// kakao에서 보낸 포맷에 맞는 데이터 처리</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h3>3. 채용 맞춤형 로드맵 로직 개발</h3>\n<br>\r\n<center>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 410px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f4578cf872acc2b963c5d72916f36eed/cb1d0/devridge_4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.729166666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f4578cf872acc2b963c5d72916f36eed/a59e9/devridge_4.webp 192w,\n/static/f4578cf872acc2b963c5d72916f36eed/0ca9f/devridge_4.webp 384w,\n/static/f4578cf872acc2b963c5d72916f36eed/a233f/devridge_4.webp 410w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 410px) 100vw, 410px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f4578cf872acc2b963c5d72916f36eed/3b721/devridge_4.png 192w,\n/static/f4578cf872acc2b963c5d72916f36eed/66595/devridge_4.png 384w,\n/static/f4578cf872acc2b963c5d72916f36eed/cb1d0/devridge_4.png 410w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 410px) 100vw, 410px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f4578cf872acc2b963c5d72916f36eed/cb1d0/devridge_4.png\"\n            alt=\"채용 맞춤형 로드맵 로직\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</center>\r\n<br>\n<p>채용 공고와 학습 자료를 결합하여 채용 공고에 맞는 로드맵을 제공하도록 로직을 개발하였습니다.</p>\n<br>\n<h1>성과</h1>\n<h2>1. 서비스 성능 약 2배 개선</h2>\n<p>채용 공고에 맞는 로드맵을 제공하기 위해 요청마다 복잡한 JOIN 연산을 수행해야 했습니다.</p>\n<p>채용 공고는 만료 기한이 정해진 데이터, 학습 데이터는 변경이 적은 데이터라 생각하였고, 이런 정적 데이터를 요청마다 연산하는 것이 리소스 낭비라고 판단하였습니다.</p>\n<br>\r\n<center>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 525px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/337abeca47f272648c30ebf806d286f8/635dd/devridge_5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.208333333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/337abeca47f272648c30ebf806d286f8/a59e9/devridge_5.webp 192w,\n/static/337abeca47f272648c30ebf806d286f8/0ca9f/devridge_5.webp 384w,\n/static/337abeca47f272648c30ebf806d286f8/bca58/devridge_5.webp 525w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/337abeca47f272648c30ebf806d286f8/3b721/devridge_5.png 192w,\n/static/337abeca47f272648c30ebf806d286f8/66595/devridge_5.png 384w,\n/static/337abeca47f272648c30ebf806d286f8/635dd/devridge_5.png 525w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/337abeca47f272648c30ebf806d286f8/635dd/devridge_5.png\"\n            alt=\"채용 맞춤형 로드맵 로직\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</center>\r\n<br>\n<p>이런 부분에서 성능 개선의 여지가 있었고, <strong>역 정규화(denormalize)</strong> 전략을 사용해서 채용 공고와 학습 자료를 사전에 결합함으로써 복잡한 JOIN 연산을 줄일 수 있었습니다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>역정규화 (Denormalization)</p>\n<p>데이터베이스의 정규화된 구조를 일부러 중복을 허용하게 하여, 조인 연산을 줄이고, 읽기 성능을 향상시키기 위한 방법입니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<br>\n<p>nGrinder를 사용해 측정해본 결과, 기존 177 TPS에서 337 TPS로 약 2배 개선된 것을 확인할 수 있었습니다.</p>\n<br>\n<h3>성능 개선 전 (Pre-optimization)</h3>\n<p>TPS : 177.1<br>\nVuser : 99, Errors : 0</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/768167b746a24e4bf589c7f220013b22/59f54/devridge_6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 39.583333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/768167b746a24e4bf589c7f220013b22/a59e9/devridge_6.webp 192w,\n/static/768167b746a24e4bf589c7f220013b22/0ca9f/devridge_6.webp 384w,\n/static/768167b746a24e4bf589c7f220013b22/dc9b9/devridge_6.webp 768w,\n/static/768167b746a24e4bf589c7f220013b22/60a83/devridge_6.webp 792w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/768167b746a24e4bf589c7f220013b22/3b721/devridge_6.png 192w,\n/static/768167b746a24e4bf589c7f220013b22/66595/devridge_6.png 384w,\n/static/768167b746a24e4bf589c7f220013b22/fe486/devridge_6.png 768w,\n/static/768167b746a24e4bf589c7f220013b22/59f54/devridge_6.png 792w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/768167b746a24e4bf589c7f220013b22/fe486/devridge_6.png\"\n            alt=\"성능 개선 전 그래프\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<h3>성능 개선 후 (Post-optimization)</h3>\n<p><strong>TPS : 337.8</strong><br>\nVuser : 99,  Errors : 0</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d224b7facd6b559b10009378ec42d127/c2252/devridge_7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 39.583333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d224b7facd6b559b10009378ec42d127/a59e9/devridge_7.webp 192w,\n/static/d224b7facd6b559b10009378ec42d127/0ca9f/devridge_7.webp 384w,\n/static/d224b7facd6b559b10009378ec42d127/dc9b9/devridge_7.webp 768w,\n/static/d224b7facd6b559b10009378ec42d127/b0930/devridge_7.webp 794w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d224b7facd6b559b10009378ec42d127/3b721/devridge_7.png 192w,\n/static/d224b7facd6b559b10009378ec42d127/66595/devridge_7.png 384w,\n/static/d224b7facd6b559b10009378ec42d127/fe486/devridge_7.png 768w,\n/static/d224b7facd6b559b10009378ec42d127/c2252/devridge_7.png 794w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d224b7facd6b559b10009378ec42d127/fe486/devridge_7.png\"\n            alt=\"성능 개선 후 그래프\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<h2>2. CI / CD 및 무중단 배포 도입</h2>\n<p>개발 과정에서 코드 통합과 배포의 효율성을 높이기 위해 CI/CD (지속적 통합 및 지속적 배포)를 도입하였습니다.</p>\n<p>CI / CD를 도입함으로써 코드의 품질을 지속적으로 관리할 수 있게 되었고, 코드 변경 사항을 신속하게 테스트하고 배포할 수 있는 체계를 구축했습니다.</p>\n<br>\n<h3>지속적 통합(CI)</h3>\n<br>\r\n<center>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 449px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0af50946a8e85de92466ba8b75d65d20/46d70/devridge_8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 26.5625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/0af50946a8e85de92466ba8b75d65d20/a59e9/devridge_8.webp 192w,\n/static/0af50946a8e85de92466ba8b75d65d20/0ca9f/devridge_8.webp 384w,\n/static/0af50946a8e85de92466ba8b75d65d20/b1433/devridge_8.webp 449w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 449px) 100vw, 449px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/0af50946a8e85de92466ba8b75d65d20/3b721/devridge_8.png 192w,\n/static/0af50946a8e85de92466ba8b75d65d20/66595/devridge_8.png 384w,\n/static/0af50946a8e85de92466ba8b75d65d20/46d70/devridge_8.png 449w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 449px) 100vw, 449px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/0af50946a8e85de92466ba8b75d65d20/46d70/devridge_8.png\"\n            alt=\"CI\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</center>\r\n<br>\n<p>이전에는 코드를 통합하는 과정에서 리뷰어와 개발자가 직접 코드를 검토해야 했기 때문에 오류가 포함된 코드가 메인 저장소에 반영되는 경우도 있었습니다.</p>\n<p>CI를 도입함으로써, 메인 저장소에 통합할 때 자동화된 빌드와 테스트가 실행되어, 코드에 문제가 있는지 신속하게 파악하고 해결할 수 있게 하였습니다.</p>\n<br>\n<h3>지속적 배포(CD)</h3>\n<br>\r\n<center>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 414px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9f9b399da922b31337b1bc8853442d1e/c6ea4/devridge_9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.52083333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/9f9b399da922b31337b1bc8853442d1e/a59e9/devridge_9.webp 192w,\n/static/9f9b399da922b31337b1bc8853442d1e/0ca9f/devridge_9.webp 384w,\n/static/9f9b399da922b31337b1bc8853442d1e/d3277/devridge_9.webp 414w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 100vw, 414px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/9f9b399da922b31337b1bc8853442d1e/3b721/devridge_9.png 192w,\n/static/9f9b399da922b31337b1bc8853442d1e/66595/devridge_9.png 384w,\n/static/9f9b399da922b31337b1bc8853442d1e/c6ea4/devridge_9.png 414w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 100vw, 414px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/9f9b399da922b31337b1bc8853442d1e/c6ea4/devridge_9.png\"\n            alt=\"CD\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</center>\r\n<br>\n<p>이전에는 코드 변경사항을 수동으로 배포해야 했기 때문에 실수나 환경 설정 문제로 인한 오류가 발생할 위험이 높았습니다.</p>\n<p>지속적인 통합(CD)을 도입하여 자동으로 배포하게 함으로써 이러한 문제들이 대폭 감소하였습니다.</p>\n<br>\n<h3>무중단 배포</h3>\n<p>서비스의 가용성을 최대화하기 위해 무중단 배포를 도입하였습니다.</p>\n<p>Blue/Green 배포는 기존 버전(Blue)과 새 버전(Green)의 서비스를 동시에 운영하며, 새 버전의 안정성을 확인한 후 트래픽을 점차적으로 이전하여 가용성을 저해하지 않고 서비스를 업데이트할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>이 방법을 통해 배포 과정에서 발생할 수 있는 다운타임을 없애고, 만약 새 버전에 문제가 발견되면 즉시 이전 버전으로 롤백할 수 있는 안전망을 마련했습니다</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>서비스 가용성</p>\n<p>얼마나 안정적으로 사용자에게 접근 가능한 상태를 유지하는지를 나타내는 지표</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1>문제와 해결</h1>\n<p>데이터가 중복적으로 발생하는 문제가 발생</p>\n<p>MVP 단계에서 배포를 중복을 허용한 상태에서 프로젝트를 열지.. 아니면 이 부분을 해결하여 코드를 수정하고 할지에 대한 고민이였는데</p>\n<p>MVP 먼저 배포하고 그 후에 수정을 진행하는 방식을 선택함</p>\n<br>\n<h1>아쉬운 점</h1>","frontmatter":{"title":"DEVRIDGE 프로젝트 회고","summary":"DEVRIDGE 프로젝트에서 성과와 부족한 점을 돌아보며 회고하는 글입니다.","date":"2024.03.20.","categories":["Review","Optimization"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/webp;base64,UklGRmwAAABXRUJQVlA4IGAAAADwAwCdASoUAAsAPp0+mkgloyKhMAgAsBOJZwC/OCB/gAv9clU1FXgAAP7x4PGIVO9dcW91cERHbXIUogt9ClWLTbTdCYYEztMpLnUHwA3mSD+z48n/aj5SsPtvgl1qAAA="},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/44a8a8fc5da673ed99505ea8f4c84fc1/a7f05/devridge_main.webp","srcSet":"/static/44a8a8fc5da673ed99505ea8f4c84fc1/41dd1/devridge_main.webp 448w,\n/static/44a8a8fc5da673ed99505ea8f4c84fc1/69efe/devridge_main.webp 896w,\n/static/44a8a8fc5da673ed99505ea8f4c84fc1/a7f05/devridge_main.webp 1792w","sizes":"(min-width: 1792px) 1792px, 100vw"},"sources":[]},"width":1792,"height":1024}},"publicURL":"/static/44a8a8fc5da673ed99505ea8f4c84fc1/devridge_main.webp"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2024_03_20_devridge/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}